title: Beyond the Horror: Asylum Episode 11
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Hi guys, I haven't been around for a few months, just had a thought.. If scathitch (Gaga/Roanoke) was the first supreme that got her powers from ancient Druidic gods, how can this be so, if the witches of Salem learned and stole their magic from tituba, and how were other supremes chosen if scathitch never died? She's immortal. The times of Roanoke and Salem must be within 100 years of each other. Am hoping for witches in s7, so nice to see you all again🤗🙂😎
